<div style="background:#7a64a8;color:#fff;padding:7px 12px;font-weight:800;font-size:.77rem;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="15" height="15" fill="none" stroke="#89b4d4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;flex-shrink:0;"><rect x="18" y="3" width="4" height="18"/><rect x="10" y="8" width="4" height="13"/><rect x="2" y="13" width="4" height="8"/></svg> 社會風險揭露</div>

